This column tracks the current events of the University of Washingtons Registered Student Organizations RSOs PERIOD The following events are courtesy of RSOs and communities on campus PERIOD



Monday Nov PERIOD 

TOSA Milk Tea  Husky Football Raffle Sale

In need of a cool beverage on the way to class Why not stop by the Taiwanese Overseas Student Association booth for milk tea TOSA will begin selling KungFU Tea for  from Monday to Friday in Red Square starting at  p.m PERIOD With every purchase theres a chance to win a raffle ticket to see the Huskies play against the Sun Devils on Nov PERIOD  PERIOD



Wednesday Nov PERIOD 

IVU Thanksgiving Extravaganza

InterVarsity Undergraduate is hosting its annual Thanksgiving dinner this week PERIOD InterVarsity seeks to provide a community for Christian students PERIOD The event will be held at the Seattle Vineyard from  p.m PERIOD



UW Relay Kickoff

The annual UW Relay Kickoff is back PERIOD Over  students take part in the relay every year to help raise funds for the American Cancer Society PERIOD There will be games as well as discounts and raffles to thank students who sign up early PERIOD The event will take place on the Quad from  p.m PERIOD



Thursday Nov PERIOD 

Cozy Autumn Humble Feast

ASUW Student Food Cooperative is celebrating the Humble Feast with locally sourced organic and sustainable food PERIOD Join the members with some chili roasted vegetables cornbread and apple crisps PERIOD All food is gluten free vegan and prepared by the members of the food coop PERIOD The event will be held at the Center of Urban Horticulture from  p.m PERIOD



Friday Nov PERIOD 

JUNAI Film Screening and QA

Global Peace Women and the JUN AI World Peace Foundation are partnering to host a film screening of JUN AI. cQ The event will be held at Kane Hall from  p.m PERIOD JUN AI is a film that explores themes of unconditional love and reconciliation between the Japanese and the Chinese PERIOD There will be a brief QA after the event PERIOD Tickets can be purchased online for  or  for students PERIOD Tickets at the door cost  and  for students PERIOD
